{"tid":1639591,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黨鐵：週三大致維持正常服務，預告仍會提早結束","createTime":"2019-10-08T16:05:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T17:37:11.000Z","uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"41aee6a37f27ae0464196d8a431aaf87891b346a","tid":1639591,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:05:06.000Z","msg":"Source: 匪報01 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae3fc08672a3b39d83263ee81025521672569246","tid":1639591,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:07:40.000Z","msg":"港鐵列車服務安排（10月9日）<br />\n<br />\n此訊息發放時間 : 2019-10-08 23:55<br />\n<br />\n經過努力復修並與警方及相關政府部門進行風險評估後，港鐵各綫明天大致維持正常列車服務，然而受嚴重破壞，部分車站仍然暫停開放，個別車站出入口或設施需要較長的復修時間。為了騰空更多時間讓車務及工程團隊繼續餘下修復工作，列車服務也會提早結束。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵待確定服務具體安排後，會於明天早上詳細公布。<br />\n<br />\n同時，我們會繼續因應實際情況和安全考慮，在提供服務的車站實施客流管理措施，或作出車務調動，包括在未能預先通知的情況下，再次關閉車站和安排列車不停車站、關閉車站出入口等。<br />\n<br />\n有關最新車務安排，請留意港鐵網頁、手機應用程式MTR Mobile、車站及列車廣播，以及電台及電視台發放的資訊。"},{"pid":"bb9a046f06e4c6d86909a4a3639af8e213c86b5d","tid":1639591,"uid":122233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:08:06.000Z","msg":"即係又8點啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96b69636b4fcdbca61a7281434df7587f3ea245f","tid":1639591,"uid":1602,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:08:45.000Z","msg":"今晚又提供場比狗同tvb 拍戲"},{"pid":"0dcf5e9c680689e5024ac55f0717be2ae088a57a","tid":1639591,"uid":28575,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:10:38.000Z","msg":"提早收車比你班卧底狗係入面爆站屈我地手足做？"},{"pid":"2dbbec6bd494c799586ee5e480e5e468d312fa59","tid":1639591,"uid":256059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T16:11:01.000Z","msg":"又 book 左場景 .....<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98721a17e25b8b48f1ee299ff72f6eb35096a695","tid":1639591,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:10:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8c782e670bd42d205fec2142f8a7b669842eeab","tid":1639591,"uid":63543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T17:37:11.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}